'''''Psychology and Developing Societies (PDS)''''' is a [[peer reviewed]] journal. This is a forum for discussion for psychologists from different parts of the world concerned with the problems of developing societies. PDS provides information in different areas of psychology. It is published twice a year by [http://www.sagepub.in/home.nav SAGE Publications]
